I believe the lines 409-411 should be removed and line 410 should be moved after line 401 - so that redirectUri is set to the redirectUri of account client just in case that it corresponds to account client? Probably something like this:
       if (client == null) {
            client = SystemClientUtil.getSystemClient(realm);
            redirectUri = Urls.accountBase(session.getContext().getUri().getBaseUri()).path("/").build(realm.getName()).toString();
        }

WDYT?

